  "briefing": "COREWARD RELIEF AUTHORITY relay: A beacon downlane is broadcasting a survivor count, a fuel state, and a heading — and no two of those numbers agree with the third. Command wants to answer it. You're the one doing the arithmetic. Decide how much of it they get to hear.",
